eamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233420/extras/07b2007fe6b9f26feef2b1a31859d8e8.mp4?t=1759666279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satanás es el encargado de Sinner’s Tavern, un lugar de reunión y descanso. Habla e interactúa con él y con todos los pecadores perdidos  que encuentres en tu travesía por el infierno.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233420/extras/2a6775e97b9a11e9d9144d696bbd9c56.poster.avif?t=1759666279\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233420/extras/2a6775e97b9a11e9d9144d696bbd9c56.webm?t=1759666279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233420/extras/2a6775e97b9a11e9d9144d696bbd9c56.mp4?t=1759666279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
